President Donald J. Trump has announced the designation of a Presidential Delegation to attend the Peace to Prosperity Workshop in Manama, Bahrain, from June 25 to June 26, 2019. The delegation will be led by Secretary of the Treasury, Steven T. Mnuchin. Other members of the delegation include Jared Kushner, Jason Greenblatt, Kevin Hassett, Brian Hook, Brent J. McIntosh, Geoffrey Okamoto, Monica E. Crowley, Avi Berkowitz, John Rader, Jennifer Nordquist, and Thomas Storch.